text: Protium may refer to: * Protium (isotope) or hydrogen-1, the most common isotope of the element hydrogen, with one proton, one electron, and no neutrons * Protium (plant), a genus of chiefly tropical American trees in the family Burseraceae, having fragrant wood * Cadence Protium, hardware accelerated prototyping platforms for early software development by Cadence Design Systems ==See also== * Protonix, a commercial name for pantoprazole, a proton pump inhibitor drug
title: Protium
